These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, magic-tricks
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, orchid
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | traveling |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| Flower     | bellflower     | orchid      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, sprite
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, june
There 2 different types of food: lime, cucumber
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Birthday   | june | september  |
| Food     | cucumber   | lime |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different pets are kept: frog, cat
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
There 2 different types of food: lemon, pepper
1. the owner of the cat is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Pet         | frog   | cat  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Food         | lemon   | pepper |

