The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, superhero
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: techno, electronic
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Nationality          | mexican | nigerian |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | fantasy   |
| Music-Genre     | electronic       | techno      |

