.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: japanese, colombian
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, car
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
3. the japanese is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality    | colombian | japanese     |
| Transport     | car | skateboard |
| Sport   | skiing | sailing    |

