.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, rat
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: surfing, water-polo
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Pet           | rat     | ferret |
| Sport   | water-polo | surfing  |
| Transport     | ship      | boat |

